        "text": "backend/app/api/mcp.py — new Flask blueprint, 291 lines, per-client pre-rendered JSON snippets; tool-catalog drift caught by regex-based unit test against mcp_server.py",
        "variant": "body"
      }
    },
    "change2": {
      "type": "Text",
      "props": {
        "text": "SettingsPanel.vue — +445 lines, clipboard API + execCommand fallback so the copy button works in non-secure contexts too",
        "variant": "body"
